'''Ciomara Otoniela Morais''' (yavutse ku ya 14 Werurwe 1984), ni umukinnyi wa filime ukomoka muri Porutugali [[Angola|wavukiye muri Angola]] ufite inkomoko ya Macanese.  Morais azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime ''Querida Preciosa'', ''[[:en:All_Is_Well_(2011_film)|All Is Well]]'' and ''A Ilha dos Cães''

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 14 Werurwe 1984 i Benguela, muri [[Angola]]. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2005, yakinnye bwa mbere muri filimi ya ''Morangos com Açúcar'' . Muri uruhererekane, uruhare rwe nka 'Salomé' rwamenyekanye cyane kandi yakiriye imirimo myinshi mumyaka iri imbere kuri tereviziyo. Bamwe muribo barimo, uruhare 'Leonor' muri ''Diário de Sofia'', uruhare 'Masara' muri ''Equador'' hanyuma muri ''Makamba Hotel'' . Hagati aho, yimukiye mu ikinamico akina umukino wa mbere ''A Balada da Margem Sul'' iyobowe na Hélder Costa. 

Yakoze sinema ye ya mbere muri firime ya 2009 ''The Abused'' afite uruhare ruto. Uruhare rwe rwa mbere muri cinema rwanyuze muri 2011 rwamamaye cyane ''All Is Well'' with the role 'Leonor'.  Yatsindiye igihembo cy'umukinnyi witwaye neza muri Festival du Cinéma Africain de Khouribga (FCAK), [[Maroke|Maroc]] na The Carthage Film Festival, [[Tunisiya|Tuniziya]] mu mwaka wa 2012 kubera uruhare yagize muri filime ''[[:en:All_Is_Well_(2011_film)|All Is Well]]'' . Muri uwo mwaka, iyi filime yatsindiye igihembo cya Filime nziza y’igiportigale mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga ryigenga rya IndieLisboa. 

Muri 2012, yerekanwe bwa mbere ''mubuyobozi no kwandika hamwe na firime ngufi Encontro com o Criador'' . Hagati aho, yanavuze kuri firime ya animasiyo 'Nayola'. 

